name: logical-unification
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "0.4.5" %}

package:
  name: logical-unification
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/l/logical-unification/logical-unification-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 7c6a6c1b7c6baa0f5b9af93f06cfc8d2419b6b793346b678ed1367c05ce74558
  patches:

build:
  number: 0
  script: {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv
  noarch: python

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python >=3.6
    - setuptools
  run:
    - python >=3.6
    - toolz
    - multipledispatch

test:
  imports:
    - unification

about:
  home: https://github.com/pythological/unification
  license: BSD-3-Clause
  summary: Logical unification in Python.
  license_file: LICENSE.txt
  dev_url: https://github.com/pythological/unification

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - brandonwillard
